io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.rsrc

Class ResourceDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.rsrc.ResourceDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    scala.Equals

    public class ResourceDirectory
extends java.lang.Object
implements scala.Equals
    Header and the entries which point to either data or other resource directory tables.

    Each ResourceDirectory therefore is also a tree consisting of more tables or resource data entries as leaves.
